Name: ns_limitregonconnect
Author: djGrrr
Category: NickServ
Last updated: 2006-10-05T06:34:33+01:00

This module protects the NickServ REGISTER and GROUP commands from being used right away when a user connects, this can be very helpful to deal with botnets that connect and register/group a bunch of nicknames.

View module header for changelog.

Version 1.00 supports Anope 1.7.14
Version 1.01 supports Anope 1.7.14
Version 1.02 supports Anope 1.7.14
Version 1.03 supports Anope 1.7.23
